        <p>The <strong>AMD Family 10h</strong>, or <strong>K10</strong>, is a microprocessor microarchitecture by <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('AMD', 'C'); ?>. Though there were once reports that the K10 had been canceled, the first third-generation <strong>Opteron</strong> products for servers were launched on 10 September 2007, with the <strong>Phenom</strong> processors for desktops following and launching on 11 November 2007 as the immediate successors to the <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('K8', 'CPU'); ?> series of processors (<?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Athlon 64', 'CPU'); ?>, Opteron, 64-bit Sempron).</p>
